        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Stasian actuators help the limbs of this full plate move of their own accord, as long as they\u2019re supplied with power. A chamber in the chest plate can hold a single bottled lightning, which takes 3 Interact actions to install.",
